				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Another very important spell in this line: Tangling Weeds.
<br />

<br />
In LDoN I have found TW to be more effective snare in many situations. Fast cast, stops MoBs from dead in their tracks at 10% instead of 20%, low mana consumption and high aggro, all make for TW to be a great spell. I have it memmed in all my spell sets.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=669557" target="_blank" class="postlink">SokkoMatic</a>
