				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Level 9 
<br />
Snare/Tangling Weeds - think tangling weeds is more aggro.
<br />
I just used snare until the spell upgrade.
<br />

<br />
Level 15
<br />
Grasping Roots - With lil dmg
<br />

<br />
Level 22
<br />
Harmony - Outdoor area calm spell
<br />
Panic - Panic animal - used in fear kiting  (saw a grouping in OT) Had multi mobs on the party.. I dont know why either of the two rangers didnt cast panic animal on the sabertooth tiger or the rhino that was pulled so could focus on the main mob. 
<br />

<br />
Level 39
<br />
Harmony of Nature - outdoor single target calm spell (still used in POV lol) I hate pulling with tanks that cant take the aggro.
<br />

<br />
Level 49
<br />
Snaring Roots - upgrade of grasping more dmg 
<br />

<br />
Level 51
<br />
Ensnare - Last of the snare spells
<br />

<br />
Level 60
<br />
Enveloping Roots - Upgrade to snaring roots 110 points of dmg
<br />

<br />
Level 63
<br />
Earthen Roots - Last of Root Spell Line<br />_________________<br />Better you than me.
